These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: pakistani, japanese, american, german, brazilian, polish, russian
1. the japanese is in the middle##1
2. the japanese is on the left of the american##1
3. the brazilian is on the right of the german##1
4. the pakistani is on the right of the american##1
5. the russian is on the far left##1
6. the polish is on the right of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Nationality   | russian | german | brazilian | japanese | american | pakistani | polish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  dressmaker, freelancer, pilot, bartender, musician, fisherman, software-developer
1. the software-developer is on the far right##1
2. the dressmaker is on the far left##1
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the musician##1
4. the musician is on the left of the pilot##1
5. the bartender is on the right of the fisherman##1
6. the software-developer is on the right of the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |    2    |      3       |   4   |     5     |   6    |    7    |
| Job   | dressmaker | musician | pilot | fisherman | bartender | freelancer | software-developer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-3::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, filmmaking, photography, camping, dancing, hiking, puzzles
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2      |   3    |    4    |      5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby   | dancing | baking | hiking | photography | puzzles | filmmaking | camping |

 #################################

 
