3. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2     |   3    |   4   |    5     |     6      |   7   |
| Pet   | chinchilla | hamster | frog | fish | horse | goat | cat |

