.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-7::.
There 7 different types of food: blueberry, pumpkin, pear, pomegranate, orange, watermelon, radish
1. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
2. the person eating orange is on the left of the person eating radish##1
3. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
4. the person eating blueberry is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the person eating orange is on the right of the person eating watermelon##1
6. the person eating radish is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3   |   4    |   5   |   6    |     7      |
| Food   | pomegranate | watermelon | orange | radish | blueberry | pumpkin | pear |

