.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-1-8::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: documentary, western, adventure, animation, zombie, musical, epic
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is in the middle##1
3. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |   4    |   5    |    6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | western | documentary | musical | animation | epic | adventure |

