2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
3. the fan of techno is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
5. the fan of dubstep is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3   |  4  |    5    |   6   |  7   |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | jazz | pop | dubstep | hip-hop | techno | indie |

